About ten people in the center of the camp were tied to each other.
And two people tied themselves to a tree, said Mr. Kelly.
Emergency services were called in to cut the locks.
There were no arrests in the park until 3:30 a.m., Mr. Kelly said.
The entire operation was completed about 75 minutes later, police said.
